Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:19.97,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}なぜ ふるえながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:25.53,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}今 求めあうの？
