Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:19.97,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}为何你在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:25.53,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}现在寻求着何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:32.16,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}只有你无论多少次
