Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.97,0:23:44.23,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}蔚蓝的星海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:50.11,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}波浪间漂浮的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:56.17,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}渐渐逝去的悲痛是
